\begin{abstract}
Recent experimental results indicate that superconductivity in Sr$_2$RuO$_4$ 
is described by the  $p$-wave $E_u$ representation 
of the $D_{4h}$ point group. Results on the vortex 
lattice structures for 
this representation are presented. The theoretical results are compared 
with experiment.

